data.description: Move in Ready 3 bedroom and 2-bathroom Home in Downtown New Port Richey. Once you get through the front door you will immediately notice the vaulted ceilings with wood beams giving the living and dining room a wide and open feeling. The Master suite has on suite bathroom with shower. The two other bedrooms are on the other side of the house and share a nice, remodeled bathroom with bathtub. Everything has been remodeled or exchanged. Kitchen appliances cabinets 2021, Roof 2021, A/C 2021, Electrical system, Pluming, Windows, Tankless Water Heater all are replaced in 2021. Just steps from this property you will find NEW PORT RICHEY AQUATIC CENTER offering: Plunge pool with giant two story, 28 foot tall water slide, Kiddie pool with zero depth entry, kiddie slide, spray fountains 2 Outdoor and 2 indoor full-court gymnasiums with wood-flooring for basketball, volleyball and pickleball, 4 Tennis court, Skate Board Park, Newly renovated Fitness Center with state of the art cardio, strength-training equipment and free weights, Indoor Playground with free Child Watch for members during certain daytime hours and More. Also, 3 minutes away you will find a spectacular place called New Port Richey Cotee River Park to enjoy a beautiful sunset or you can fish by boat or from the shore. Don't miss this opportunity to enjoy Fl lifestyle. The Approved construction plans are in the property. Survey ATTACHED
